  "sd.aiInt.faq1.a": { en: "We support sales assistants, content assistants, SOP assistants, and workflow-specific agents tailored to your operations.", es: "Soportamos asistentes de ventas, contenido, SOPs y agentes espec\u00edficos de flujos adaptados a tus operaciones.", fr: "Nous supportons les assistants de vente, contenu, SOP et agents sp\u00e9cifiques aux flux adapt\u00e9s \u00e0 vos op\u00e9rations." },
